(THE AXIOMS) show newline
(------------------------------------------------------------------------) show newline
() show newline
() show newline
(    A1. No Ambient Authority) show newline
(        You have nothing until someone gives you something.) show newline
(        Every access requires presenting a capability.) show newline
(    A2. Capabilities Are Unforgeable) show newline
(        Ed25519 signatures. No exceptions.) show newline
(        Create by origin or delegation. No other path.) show newline
(    A3. Capabilities Only Attenuate) show newline
(        Delegation can reduce rights, never amplify.) show newline
(        What you give cannot exceed what you hold.) show newline
(    A4. Objects Are Immutable Content) show newline
(        SHA-512 hash IS identity.) show newline
(        No metadata. No labels. No ACLs.) show newline
(        Objects don't know who can access them.) show newline
